In the past year many adventurers have reported that a town exists in
the once declared uninhabitable plains of western Hyperborea. These
same adventurers report sightings of supernatural beings. Some say
they are ghosts, others say demons, but no one knows for sure. There
is a rumor that this hidden town was cursed long ago. Although, this
is only a rumor. This quest involves seeking out this supernatural
town, discovering the truth behind its existance, and fulfilling the
request of its citizens.

This quest involves no combat, although it does require careful
attention to detail and slight exploration. Feel free to try it at 
any level.
